=== CONDITIONS ===
{
  "_": "Conditions. What is true right now. OVERWRITE this block each cycle — do not append entries. Write one short sentence per key describing current reality. If nothing changed, say so. If the purpose leaf is satisfied, say that. This is a snapshot, not a diary."
}
