{
  "_": "History. The positive temporal coordinate — curated record of what happened. Form 2: backward-facing. Logarithmic compression, base 9. Each node fills digits 1-9; when full, Haiku summarises into parent underscore and the cascade continues. Ground truth lives in the filmstrip; this is the entity's own memory — what it chose to remember."
